name: MerongstelMix
description:
MerongstelMix is a mixture model made with merongmix++ and pastelmix.

You can generate images similar to "merongmix++" with a more anime(?) style.

I highly recommend using

  • highres.fix(or generation with high-resolution)

  • higher sampling step >40 (low sampling step for the second pass is OK)

  • Negative prompts "(low quality, worst quality:1.4)" or more

  • VAE: kl-f8-anime2.vae.pt, 840000-ema-pruned.vae.pt and anything-v4.0.vae.pt

    • Up to your decision

Also, you can find other models:

  • merongmix+ | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

  • merongmix++ | Stable Diffusion Checkpoint | Civitai

And my ai artwork:

  • cinoai User Profile | DeviantArt

  • 下手て - pixiv

  • cinoaiAIART (@cinoaiaiai) / Twitter

  • 아멜리아최고 - Twitch

Thanks!

The metadata for the sample image was missing, possibly due to a problem with WEBP files. I restored them one by one, but some metadata may not have been restored. Please let me know if you find any missing data.

Also, all sample images for merongstelmix(not merongsteline) are generated with

  • Steps: 45

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras

  • CFG scale: 11

  • Denoising strength: 0.4

  • Clip skip: 2

  • ENSD: 31337

  • Hires upscale: 2

  • Hires steps: 15

  • Hires upscaler: R-ESRGAN 4x+ Anime6B

For merongsteline

  • Steps: 30

  • Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras

  • CFG scale: 9

  • Size: 640x960

  • Denoising strength: 0.4

  • Clip skip: 2

  • ENSD: 31337

  • Hires upscale: 1.5

  • Hires steps: 15

  • Hires upscaler: Lanczos
